{"tid":1687230,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要]呢個方法可以救到好多前線手足！！！","createTime":"2019-11-01T16:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-03T00:49:32.000Z","uid":110079,"like":47,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":29,"replies":[{"pid":"73d78f6a21311b225d87a3882e6b38dc90711851","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"觀察過夢境裏咁多場大大小小嘅示威<br />\n我發覺係同狗對陣嘅時候有個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好大嘅毛病</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就係狗衝過嚟咬人嘅時候，手足就即刻拔腳狂奔，顧唔到身邊人，搞到好多跑得慢尤其是係女仔就咁俾狗咬咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望大家慎重考慮昔日用過既戰術<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">遮陣人牆！！！</span></span><br />\n你可能會話，咪傻啦咩年代呀仲用遮陣<br />\n但係試諗下，6.12 721甚至係以前雨傘嗰陣，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>有幾何會俾狗咬走咗?</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原因係條防線夠厚<br />\n狗唔可以大規模衝擊<br />\n前排手足用遮陣，遠則擋住橡膠子彈，近則阻止胡椒同棍嘅攻勢<br />\n後排搭膊頭，拉實前排<br />\n再加上依家進化咗嘅火魔磚雨強力遠程支援底下</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁多位勇武手足絕對可以全身而退</span></span><br />\n比起依家遇狗就好似動物大遷徙咁逃難 <br />\n依個係唯一救人救己嘅團體力量<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">體現真正既齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n從今日起<br />\n大家叫既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔單止係企鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係前線企密啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔淨止係手足走快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係數一二面對敵人向後撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，冇一個戰術係完美既，有幾個主意事項<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 叫手足企密啲嘅話，會唔會好難走?</strong></ins><br />\n企鬆啲固然一定要，為咗防止走得急會人踩人，但只限於後排嘅手足。<span style=\"color: green;\">前線企越密防守力越強</span>，有如古代羅馬方陣攻守兼備，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更變相少咗個藉口俾前中排遇狗即走 揼低企最前/走得慢嘅手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2.依家都唔玩陣地戰，用遊擊方法做完即走唔會好啲咩?</strong></ins><br />\n無錯，實力懸殊當然要遊擊，但係有時世事無咁如意。試諗下大規模嘅遊行甚至遍地開花嘅時候，人數點止幾百人?咁多人係無可能走得切。更何況，<strong>「be water」</strong> 既真諦係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">靈活變通   因時制宜<br />\n時而化整為零 逐個擊破<br />\n時而固若金湯 穩如泰山<br />\n剛柔並濟 方為上上策</span></span><br />\n係大戰場，保護大家既方法就係要密集防禦，對敵人嘅攻擊寸步不讓，甚至有反撲之勢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3.咁係咪人多嘅時候遮陣人鏈最好？</ins></strong><br />\n正如頭先所講，冇一個策略係完美既，要根據當時情況行動。就例如水炮車嚟到又或者被包抄，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係無足夠既防禦準備情況下</span>全速撤退係需要嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人唔主張硬碰硬<br />\n但絕對唔可以將人數優勢白白浪費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 閣下有少少嘅祝福俾咁多位同行兒女<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運昌隆 得償所願<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要抗爭 直至勝利嘅一刻！！！</span></span>"},{"pid":"0e090a981ecef7a6b23ca2f170c4efccbfcdd5f3","tid":1687230,"uid":263058,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:29:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d1487a8a9b71b00c199afd67822d20bcf64d8291","tid":1687230,"uid":134054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:30:19.000Z","msg":"「習近平，甴近平， 曱甴王」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n112 「求援國際 堅守自治」公民活動日真正run down如下：<br />\n<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 到維園支持 逾100位候選人合法選舉聚會<br />\n- 3pm - 5pm: 環保方式前往 中環<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環愛丁堡廣場一帶 （美國集會已批不反）<br />\n- 5pm: 塞爆 中環遮打花園一帶 （紙鶴活動已批不反）"},{"pid":"e1e229f7bd0c30286517eda354ebe77c95ae7de5","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:30:22.000Z","msg":"推 救人要緊1/10"},{"pid":"5022d9dc062d0370b8707533f3ea012462863aa6","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:30:33.000Z","msg":"推 救人要緊2/10"},{"pid":"4815f6257d41c385088721fee1366554ad0cb1ae","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:30:51.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"0180f65421eee38c74fab04982901c0af5cfa264","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:31:02.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"e9d2bad4f5abd60990c58c669a9570c0bb62fb9c","tid":1687230,"uid":154767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:31:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0a1cc4774d733b99e3ba184c37fbbe500f11207","tid":1687230,"uid":36121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"如果你個post早啲出 應該會多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6c697232802006347f0f5e6324bdf970de11a1","tid":1687230,"uid":67006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2061ead2c98ea9068c405df065fd9d5c7bb55922","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0a1cc4774d733b99e3ba184c37fbbe500f11207","tid":1687230,"uid":36121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:31:24.000Z","msg":"如果你個post早啲出 應該會多啲人睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:33:55.000Z","msg":"因為我想班狗少啲時間部處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得嘅話係tg share 出去<br />\n救返多啲手足"},{"pid":"eb4ec8d10333d3c1bbf32dd80f34c404a71ab864","tid":1687230,"uid":36121,"like":0,