 style=\"color: red;\">原因係條防線夠厚<br />\n狗唔可以大規模衝擊<br />\n前排手足用遮陣，遠則擋住橡膠子彈，近則阻止胡椒同棍嘅攻勢<br />\n後排搭膊頭，拉實前排<br />\n再加上依家進化咗嘅火魔磚雨強力遠程支援底下</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁多位勇武手足絕對可以全身而退</span></span><br />\n比起依家遇狗就好似動物大遷徙咁逃難 <br />\n依個係唯一救人救己嘅團體力量<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">體現真正既齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n從今日起<br />\n大家叫既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔單止係企鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係前線企密啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔淨止係手足走快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係數一二面對敵人向後撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，冇一個戰術係完美既，有幾個主意事項<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 叫手足企密啲嘅話，會唔會好難走?</strong></ins><br />\n企鬆啲固然一定要，為咗防止走得急會人踩人，但只限於後排嘅手足。<span style=\"color: green;\">前線企越密防守力越強</span>，有如古代羅馬方陣攻守兼備，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更變相少咗個藉口俾前中排遇狗即走 揼低企最前/走得慢嘅手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2.依家都唔玩陣地戰，用遊擊方法做完即走唔會好啲咩?</strong></ins><br />\n無錯，實力懸殊當然要遊擊，但係有時世事無咁如意。試諗下大規模嘅遊行甚至遍地開花嘅時候，人數點止幾百人?咁多人係無可能走得切。更何況，<strong>「be water」</strong> 既真諦係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">靈活變通   因時制宜<br />\n時而化整為零 逐個擊破<br />\n時而固若金湯 穩如泰山<br />\n剛柔並濟 方為上上策</span></span><br />\n係大戰場，保護大家既方法就係要密集防禦，對敵人嘅攻擊寸步不讓，甚至有反撲之勢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3.咁係咪人多嘅時候遮陣人鏈最好？</ins></strong><br />\n正如頭先所講，冇一個策略係完美既，要根據當時情況行動。就例如水炮車嚟到又或者被包抄，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係無足夠既防禦準備情況下</span>全速撤退係需要嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人唔主張硬碰硬<br />\n但絕對唔可以將人數優勢白白浪費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 閣下有少少嘅祝福俾咁多位同行兒女<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運昌隆 得償所願<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要抗爭 直至勝利嘅一刻！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:40:17.000Z","msg":"【112 流水式集會】Last Minutes 攻略<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1687153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1687153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a04210575c41a311cedba69dc709b421d1944376","tid":1687230,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"其實一開始話要死守係因為要D狗清場一次難過一次 <br />\n前線有無諗過仲有無需要咁做?"},{"pid":"e6d8882ac19762cc83bb82f98f7536d80021041c","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"596d4cb68fa650ace408d89a73f2f28419e6a802","tid":1687230,"uid":273772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"睇下幾多人啦，<br />\n呢個post講既唔係唔得，<br />\n不過係入坑post，<br />\n要有獻身準備。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:42:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79759dc4bf5c2c0e02040b7715592109d2c113ed","tid":1687230,"uid":48093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:43:29.000Z","msg":"以前仲有盾 武器都話仲有得擋下...<br />\n但依家好多時乜都無  出到去都比狗搜哂"},{"pid":"b235f6145386c5d9b597bfaabde0f56c26a20ed4","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04210575c41a311cedba69dc709b421d1944376","tid":1687230,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"其實一開始話要死守係因為要D狗清場一次難過一次 <br />\n前線有無諗過仲有無需要咁做?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:44:27.000Z","msg":"如果有反擊嘅心態嘅就會<br />\n但係依家大家只系嗌口號而唔行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bf2dfe347ff8cee759f1d3443c41adc075b75d4","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:46:24.000Z","msg":"所以可以嘅話 RB在前人在後 趁班曱甴焗住落車拆RB時退後<br />\n如果拆得快 班曱甴會衝過嚟 到時再用遮陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"846e974be8ee9f90566b2d734c39a10566ceb1cf","tid":1687230,"uid":36121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a04210575c41a311cedba69dc709b421d1944376","tid":1687230,"uid":29381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:42:40.000Z","msg":"其實一開始話要死守係因為要D狗清場一次難過一次 <br />\n前線有無諗過仲有無需要咁做?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:48:40.000Z","msg":"你可能會話，咪傻啦咩年代呀仲用遮陣<br />\n但係試諗下，6.12 721甚至係以前雨傘嗰陣，有幾何會俾狗咬走咗? <br />\n樓主嘅意思好似唔係要死守 而係整個陣慢慢退 真係齊上齊落 減少變做跑online<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bffddc4f36133026dfe2deffb41f66cb0af113e8","tid":1687230,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8bf545bd77537934e6e3983847d6c6af51ea79d7","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bffddc4f36133026dfe2deffb41f66cb0af113e8","tid":1687230,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:50:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"所以就係要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋依家前中排都夠gear唔會好似以前咁怕食煙<br />\n最緊要大家要有個共識係齊上齊落唔揼低任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23383376a7d397ddfab2b18394337a61a495e914","tid":1687230,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf545bd77537934e6e3983847d6c6af51ea79d7","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bffddc4f36133026dfe2deffb41f66cb0af113e8","tid":1687230,"uid":175346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0