"msg":"但係任何時候呢個都系其中一個防咬抗打戰術<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以咪話要大家有個共識先去做<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我都唔想因為少人做而害咗佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb5192a7a3d21c072a5a8d6289248055564f382","tid":1687230,"uid":273772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b78d28265ea7547986d86affd2d987a63750ed42","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"23383376a7d397ddfab2b18394337a61a495e914","tid":1687230,"uid":29381,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf545bd77537934e6e3983847d6c6af51ea79d7","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:52:44.000Z","msg":"所以就係要團結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋依家前中排都夠gear唔會好似以前咁怕食煙<br />\n最緊要大家要有個共識係齊上齊落唔揼低任何人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:54:25.000Z","msg":"最後一定送晒成班前線去死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:57:24.000Z","msg":"仲記唔記得6.12<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然無裝 實力懸殊<br />\n但係大家真係齊上齊落架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T17:12:25.000Z","msg":"時勢唔同啦ching，仲講612，仲一樣咩。。啲狗癲既程度都唔一樣啦"},{"pid":"dc7d57c861432c6dd95b0e9099e2afdf8edc72d5","tid":1687230,"uid":177731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"73d78f6a21311b225d87a3882e6b38dc90711851","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T16:28:19.000Z","msg":"觀察過夢境裏咁多場大大小小嘅示威<br />\n我發覺係同狗對陣嘅時候有個<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">好大嘅毛病</span></span><br />\n<br />\n就係狗衝過嚟咬人嘅時候，手足就即刻拔腳狂奔，顧唔到身邊人，搞到好多跑得慢尤其是係女仔就咁俾狗咬咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以，我希望大家慎重考慮昔日用過既戰術<br />\n就係 <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">遮陣人牆！！！</span></span><br />\n你可能會話，咪傻啦咩年代呀仲用遮陣<br />\n但係試諗下，6.12 721甚至係以前雨傘嗰陣，<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>有幾何會俾狗咬走咗?</strong></span> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">原因係條防線夠厚<br />\n狗唔可以大規模衝擊<br />\n前排手足用遮陣，遠則擋住橡膠子彈，近則阻止胡椒同棍嘅攻勢<br />\n後排搭膊頭，拉實前排<br />\n再加上依家進化咗嘅火魔磚雨強力遠程支援底下</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">咁多位勇武手足絕對可以全身而退</span></span><br />\n比起依家遇狗就好似動物大遷徙咁逃難 <br />\n依個係唯一救人救己嘅團體力量<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">體現真正既齊上齊落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n從今日起<br />\n大家叫既<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔單止係企鬆啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係前線企密啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">唔淨止係手足走快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><span style=\"color: red;\">而係數一二面對敵人向後撤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n當然，冇一個戰術係完美既，有幾個主意事項<br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>1. 叫手足企密啲嘅話，會唔會好難走?</strong></ins><br />\n企鬆啲固然一定要，為咗防止走得急會人踩人，但只限於後排嘅手足。<span style=\"color: green;\">前線企越密防守力越強</span>，有如古代羅馬方陣攻守兼備，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">更變相少咗個藉口俾前中排遇狗即走 揼低企最前/走得慢嘅手足</span><br />\n<br />\n<ins><strong>2.依家都唔玩陣地戰，用遊擊方法做完即走唔會好啲咩?</strong></ins><br />\n無錯，實力懸殊當然要遊擊，但係有時世事無咁如意。試諗下大規模嘅遊行甚至遍地開花嘅時候，人數點止幾百人?咁多人係無可能走得切。更何況，<strong>「be water」</strong> 既真諦係<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">靈活變通   因時制宜<br />\n時而化整為零 逐個擊破<br />\n時而固若金湯 穩如泰山<br />\n剛柔並濟 方為上上策</span></span><br />\n係大戰場，保護大家既方法就係要密集防禦，對敵人嘅攻擊寸步不讓，甚至有反撲之勢<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>3.咁係咪人多嘅時候遮陣人鏈最好？</ins></strong><br />\n正如頭先所講，冇一個策略係完美既，要根據當時情況行動。就例如水炮車嚟到又或者被包抄，<span style=\"font-size: large;\">係無足夠既防禦準備情況下</span>全速撤退係需要嘅<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">個人唔主張硬碰硬<br />\n但絕對唔可以將人數優勢白白浪費</span></span><br />\n<br />\n最後 閣下有少少嘅祝福俾咁多位同行兒女<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">武運昌隆 得償所願<br />\n光復香港 時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我哋要抗爭 直至勝利嘅一刻！！！</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:42:05.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"ab77a1c4e75c620dd928f1cf50808ef48bbc5e81","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:44:59.000Z","msg":"繼續推5/10"},{"pid":"8a24b40256af9a1a81db789c074492aefdf217be","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"fba52f48edf72f4a3224f172ccffa21567227eb6","tid":1687230,"uid":110079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:45:20.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"93624d5017f5dfd127fb021066faae206b4e1b69","tid":1687230,"uid":336903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c87add3ffd488eb4e8b9cd9821f8e9f9291c558","tid":1687230,"uid":336903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:51:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"926ada0c93d4ed96aba8b53323acd0874a51e763","tid":1687230,"uid":336903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}